    "This fluidity not only makes the writing process more efficient but also makes it more dynamic and responsive.",
    "The scope of feedback provided by platforms like ChatGPT is another area where their transformative potential becomes evident.",
    "Itgoes beyond grammar checks or vocabulary suggestions by addressing intricate complexities of academic writing."
